{"TopicId":222608,"ForumId":208,"TopicTitle":"Skybox changes position when vehicle launched from Kerbin ascends past 21km","CreatedByName":"krbvax","CreatedById":231742,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-05T10:12:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"krbvax","CreatedById":231742,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-05T10:12:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Wine 9.0-rc3 on Linux | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ryzen 7 | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA 3060 Ti | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen launching a vehicle from Kerbin, the starfield suddenly changes appearance when the vehicle ascends past an altitude of approximately 21km.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m reporting this as a separate bug since it has different visible symptoms, but the root cause may be the same as this bug:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022178610\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6894714094\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/221505-screen-flashes-to-black-and-parachutes-suddenly-change-position-upon-floating-origin-reset-at-21km/?do=embed\u0026amp;comment=4351844\u0026amp;embedComment=4351844\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-4351844\u0022 style=\u0022height:261px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeverity:\u003C/strong\u003E Low\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESteps to reproduce:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoad and launch the stock Kerbal-K1 vehicle.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nPoint the camera upward (radially out from Kerbin).\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nObserve the starfield as the vehicle ascends.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EExpected behavior:\u003C/strong\u003E The appearance of the starfield (ignoring atmospheric effects) remains constant.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EObserved behavior:\u003C/strong\u003E The appearance of the starfield changes suddenly when passing an altitude of 21500m.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=21km.mp4\u0026amp;fileKey=%5B!AES128GCM%5B7O84PEAdEnPe8l74ELv8r8ifsZ5/5fObZucEsbYAJSRCZgTaVnhWDtaQy1KSNNZ2np//WO4D3Hq%2BY0MTzg==%5D%5B097b935f6c91f355eaadb7d0%5D%5B98b150662656891f2d40c922907e4407%5D%5D\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E21km.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-01-05T16:26:56Z\u0022 title=\u002201/05/2024 04:26  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jan 5\u0022\u003EJanuary 5\u003C/time\u003E by The Space Peacock\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}